FBIS4-25901 "drchi116_a_94006" FBIS-CHI-94-116 Daily Report 16 Jun 1994 INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS General Foreign Ministry Holds Weekly News Conference Foreign Ministry Holds Weekly News Conference Li Peng To Visit Europe OW1606091094 Beijing XINHUA in English 0853 GMT 16 Jun 94 OW1606091094 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, June 16 (XINHUA) -- Premier Li Peng will pay official visits to the Republic of Austria, the Federal Republic of Germany and Romania form June 29 to July 12, a Chinese Foreign Ministry spokesman announced at a weekly press conference here this afternoon. According to the spokesman, the Chinese premier will pay visits to the three above countries at the invitation of Austrian Prime Minister Franz Vranitzky, German Chancellor Helmut Kohl, and Romanian President Ion Iliescu and Prime Minster Nicolae Vacaroiu.
